==Description==

The Mage is the master of the elements, wielding ice, fire, and lightning (so far). 

==Main Purpose==
The Mage serves as a high damage-dealing class.

==Statistics==
The Mage uses primarily Magic, and has a Mana statistic to augment this.

=== Prerequisites ===
None

=== Skills ===
Magic: 
  * [Fire]
  * [Ice]
  * [Lightning]

